         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">September 22nd 1882. ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ The very kind expressions of consideration for the interests of this Institution conveyed in your esteemed favor under date 20th Sept. instant ¶  forbid that I should ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.09.22</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Andrew Berry</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Letter press copy book, p. 474, School of Mines and Industries, Ballarat, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">September 22nd 1882.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The very kind expressions of consideration for the interests of this Institution conveyed in your esteemed favor under date 20th Sept. instant<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found.</p>
               </note> forbid that I should delay to reply by making my personal acknowledgments, and in anticipation of instructions to the same effect, I am sure that I am warranted in tendering you the most grateful acknowledgments of the Council also, for the invaluable service you have rendered, and the obligations you have so generously imposed. The Council never contemplated other than defraying the expenses of the gentlemen who have given their services and their time to deliver this Winter Course of Lectures.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See A. Berry to M, 19 September 1882 (in this edition as 82-09-19a).</p>
               </note> — You may rest assured that they will entertain a very deep sense of indebtedness to you when your letter is submitted for their consideration. —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Enclosed herewith I have the pleasure to hand you a note from Professor Krausé.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Note not found.</p>
               </note> Professor Smith<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Alfred Mica Smith. No letter from Smith has been found.</p>
               </note> has intimated his intention of writing to you early</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Believe me</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours most Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Andw Berry</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Acting Registrar</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron von Mueller K.C.M.G.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">&amp;c. <space unit="chars" quantity="4"/>&amp;c. <space unit="chars" quantity="4"/>&amp;c.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
